214
00:23:01,680 --> 00:23:02,920
<font color="#ffff00">Aku suka Kakak Zhuang.</font>

215
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:07,200
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kabar, Kakak Zhuang?/
