222
00:23:40,080 --> 00:23:41,880
<font color="#ffff00">A Si mendadak muncul.</font>

223
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:47,760
<font color="#ffff00">Kami pergi dulu./ Kamu bisa.</font>

224
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:57,420
<font color="#ffff00">Kak./ Kamu ini! Sudah bosan hidup? Apa
