248
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:58,920
<font color="#ffff00">Bukankah selama ini kalian pas sepadannya?</font>

249
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,000
<font color="#ffff00">Shan-cai, sudah waktunya.</font>

250
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:20,480
<font color="#ffff00">Biar aku.</font>

251
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:48,000
<font color="#ffff00">Shan-cai. Maaf, aku tahu
