00:28:28,840 --> 00:28:32,520
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah, ini benar?</font>

266
00:28:34,729 --> 00:28:36,775
<font color="#ffff00">Bicaralah.</font>

267
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:46,160
<font color="#ffff00">Shan-cai, Ayah terlalu terobsesi.</font>

268
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:51,040
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak seharusnya Ayah serakah,
