303
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:50,840
<font color="#ffff00">Ambil.</font>

304
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:58,740
<font color="#ffff00">Dao Ming-si, ini…</font>

305
00:32:59,535 --> 00:33:01,954
<font color="#ffff00">Benar-benar berterima kasih padamu.</font>

306
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:10,240
<font color="#ffff00">Lalu bagaimana aku membayarnya padamu?/
